 {\super\cf2\fs24 26}When David came to Ziklag, he sent some of the spoil to the elders of Judah, his friends, saying, \uc1\u8220*See! a present for you from the spoil of the enemies of the {\scaps Lord}, {\super\cf2\fs24 27}to them who were in Bethel, in Ramoth in the South Country, in Jattir, {\super\cf2\fs24 28}in Aroer, in Siphmoth, and to them who were in Eshtemoa, {\super\cf2\fs24 29}in Carmel, in the cities of Jerahmeelites, in the cities of the Kenites, {\super\cf2\fs24 30}in Hormah, Bor-ashan, in Athach, {\super\cf2\fs24 31}in Hebron, and to those in all the places where David and his men had stayed. 
